","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250420012725-jyayjl0","updated":"20250420013018"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"也可以直接在数据湖中的文件上运行典型的数据仓库工作负载（SQL查询和商业分析），以及数据科学/机器学习工作负载，这种架构被称为数据湖仓。"}]},{"ID":"20250420012729-5499n7c","Type":"NodeThematicBreak","Properties":{"id":"20250420012729-5499n7c","updated":"20250420012729"}},{"ID":"20250420013058-ikrv4tn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250420013058-ikrv4tn","updated":"20250420013138"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在某些情况下，分析系统的输出会提供给业务系统，可以称为"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"反向ETL"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"，分析系统输出也被称为"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"数据产品"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"}]},{"ID":"20250420140918-sdgfou4","Type":"NodeThematicBreak","Properties":{"id":"20250420140918-sdgfou4","updated":"20250420140918"}},{"ID":"20250420021412-qtnbzhh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250420021412-qtnbzhh","updated":"20250420141450"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"事件流：在几秒钟的数量级对流式传输来的数据进行分析。"}]},{"ID":"20250420141758-5zqdpah","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20250420141758-5zqdpah","updated":"20250423235616"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"云数据系统"}]},{"ID":"20250420154640-ccj10wk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250420154640-ccj10wk","updated":"20250420154845"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"使用云服务的优缺点显而易见"}]},{"ID":"20250420154846-2ynnqmi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250420154846-2ynnqmi","updated":"20250420210723"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://syc-test111.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/image-20250420154846-2720ewv.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{